OL,4,CInfected blood victims have waited too
OL,5,Clong - Shapps
OL,6,GPeople affected by the NHS infected
OL,7,Gblood scandal have waited "far too
OL,8,Glong" for answers, the defence
OL,9,Gsecretary has said.
OL,11,FGrant Shapps told the BBC families had
OL,12,Fbeen let down "over decades".
OL,14,FThe final inquiry report into what is
OL,15,Fconsidered to be the worst treatment
OL,16,Fdisaster in the history of the health
OL,17,Fservice is due on Monday.
OL,19,FAround 3,000 people given infected
OL,20,Fblood by the health service in the
OL,21,F1970s and 80s have already died.
